  npcName: ' Android 279 Visual Recording'
  npcPortrait: {fileID: -7527145504033472756, guid: 825e5e048a8143243b717d861dcc3cbd, type: 3}
  dialogueLines:
  - 'Backup Recording of Human Retrieval. Recovering now. '
  - Android 279, do you copy?
  - '[Android 279 is seen to be tending to a body.] '
  - '[The body was recovered not so far from a close-by laboratory.] '
  - '[Not so far from the laboratory explosion.]'
  - 'Copy, I am tending to a human. I believe there is hope for recovery. '
  - "Mr. \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588, Please live. You\u2019ve fixed my heart
    and my components many times. "
  - "I\u2019ve proved to be your most loyal Android.  "
  - 'I am your prized possession. '
  - 'It is now my turn to fix your components.  '
  - '. . . '
  - Shame, why does your components look different to mine?
  - "I will work hard to help you Mr. \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588.  "
